research/history/logs/agent_round_0185.stdout.log:1094:research/history/logs/agent_action_0182.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(r(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `h(x)` 是共享低秩 coarse bottleneck，`{u_i}` 是 shared/coarse 分支的静态向量库，`r(x)=x-x_coarse` 表示经第一阶段 shared/coarse 重构后的残差，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert residual 子库的静态原子；在线侧先用极便宜的 shared low-rank/coarse 分支吃掉平滑主干，再让少量 routed experts 只做静态 residual 子库上的有限加权和，因此仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared/coarse 查表 + routed residual expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能作为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前额外提示已把问题收束到“保持 very short active path，同时增大总容量，并让 shared/coarse branch 负责主干、routed experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”；在已知 `expert_topk` 与 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 都给出新的低成本负信号后，当前最有信息量的下一问不是继续在同一 family 补 `K/LATENTS`，而是用一个真正改变‘容量与激活路径关系’的结构槽位做 matched architecture probe。相对 r165 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=108`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试“cheap shared/coarse + routed residual cleanup”是否比近期失败的 routed-only / fully-factorized 方向更接近当前 low-cost anchors。本地成本自检显示该候选在当前 1024x4096 proxy 下 selection_accesses=647168、deployment_accesses=442368、combined_accesses=1089536，对应 combined_ratio 约 `0.26x`，略高于主战场上沿但明确处于允许的 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内，也显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 在约 `0.26x` 下把 FVU 压到接近或优于其历史 `K=112` 结果，并明显优于最近的 routed-only / fully-factorized probes，则下一轮可保持该 family 不变，只改 `K=96` 或 `K=112`，确认它在低成本辅助带的 deployment knee。","如果该点仍明显弱于当前 `shared_routed_expert_topk` anchors，且也不能优于 r176/r177，则可更明确地下调当前 target 上两段式 shared-lowrank residual-expert 方向优先级，转向别的 very-light residual / factorized 槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["`shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 的 LUTurbo 导出形式应按 `扩展兼容` 处理：静态 shared/coarse 库加静态 routed residual expert 子库上的有限加权和。","本轮是 architecture-level probe，不是继续在 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 主线内补 `K/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 插值。","最近低成本 probes 已给出负信号：r176 的 routed-only `expert_topk` 在约 `0.20x` 下仍明显偏弱，r177 的 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 在约 `0.20x` 下更差；当前这一步是更符合新策略提示的“cheap shared/coarse + residual experts”结构测试。","本地成本自检：在 r165 的 recipe 上切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 后，selection_accesses=647168、deployment_accesses=442368、combined_accesses=1089536，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 total_cost 约 `0.26x`，处于当前允许的辅助对照带。","该 family 的历史低成本点并非纯负信号：r144 `K=112` 曾到 `FVU≈0.1400`，r156 `K=96` 曾到 `FVU≈0.1462`，说明它至少值得用当前更相关的 low-cost anchor recipe 做一次 fresh matched validation。"],"reference_round":165,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r165 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。虽然当前阶段强调 `<0.25x` 主战场，但在最近两轮已经连续否定 routed-only 与 fully-factorized low-cost 变体后，用一个仍留在 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内、且真正改变“shared 主干 vs residual cleanup”分工关系的结构槽位做 probe，信息增量高于继续在线性 `K/LATENTS` 轴上补点。选择 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 而不是 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，是因为它更贴合本轮新增提示里“先用极便宜 shared/coarse branch 吃掉平滑主干，再让 routed experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”的结构假设。主要风险是该 family 属于已被部分下调优先级的 shared-lowrank/two-stage 类别；但它是当前仍处在低成本辅助带、且与最新策略提示最匹配的现成结构。","summary":"以 r165 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，做一轮约 `0.26x` 的辅助带 architecture probe。目标是直接回答：把 cheap shared/coarse branch 明确改成主干表示、只让 routed experts 做 sparse residual cleanup，是否比最近失败的 routed-only / fully-factorized 低成本方向更接近当前 anchors。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0185.stdout.log:1095:research/history/logs/agent_round_0106.stdout.log:200:  2. 防重复：如果同一 family 的同一结构假设连续 2 轮结果接近且未形成新非支配点，下一轮必须换轴或换 family；当前不要再重复 `factorized_expert_topk` 或 routed-only `ACTIVE_EXPERTS>1`。
research/history/logs/agent_round_0185.stdout.log:1096:research/history/logs/agent_round_0106.stdout.log:201:  3. 后续高优先级新 family 可直接参考 DeepSeek 风格异构 MoE：区分 `shared experts` 与 `routed experts`，让 shared experts 始终激活、每个 token 再额外路由少量 expert（例如 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1-4），必要时再叠 low-rank trunk 或 residual cleanup。不要把 `expert_topk ACTIVE_EXPERTS>1` 这类同质 experts 的负信号外推为对 `shared+routed experts` 的否定；如果现有 family 不支持 shared experts，应优先新增最小可运行原型，而不是继续用 `factorized_expert_topk` 充当长期替身。
